Add the following to your bash profile file.

export COUNIT_HOME=...path to counit directory...
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$COUNIT_HOME/bin/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$COUNIT_HOME/glog/lib/:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
export BOOST_ROOT=$HOME/Repository/boost_1_48_0

To install counit (including glog, pintool, etc.)
$COUNIT_HOME/scripts/install_counit.sh

To compile and install the pintool
$COUNIT_HOME/scripts/install_pintool.sh

To compile and install glog
$COUNIT_HOME/scripts/install_glog.sh
